<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PThead19</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/>Οὐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>λερίῳ Ζίπερ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> τῷ διαση<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μοτ</unclear>άτῳ ἡγεμόνι 

    <lb n="2"/>Ἡρκουλίας Αἰγύπτου 

    <lb n="3"/>παρὰ Α<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ὐ</unclear>ρηλίου Αἰθίοπα Κάνιτος ἀφήλικος μετὰ κηδεμόνος Σακαῶνος προσγενοῦς 

    <lb n="4"/>πατρικο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῦ</supplied> ἀπὸ κώμης Θεαδελφίας τοῦ Αρσινοΐτου. τοὺς ἀδικουμένους 

    <lb n="5"/>ὀρφανο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ύς</supplied>, ἡγεμὼν δέσποτα, ἐκδικεῖν εἴωθεν τὸ μεγαλεῖον τὸ σόν. 

    <lb n="6"/>ἑαυτὸς τοί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>υν ὀρφανὸς <choice><corr>καταλελειμμένος</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">καταλελιμμενης</add><del rend="corrected">καταλελιμμε<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ης</del></subst></sic></choice> στερηθεὶς ἑκατέρων τῶν γονέων 

    <lb n="7"/>οὐκ ὀλίγ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ον</supplied> ἀδικοῦμαι ὑπὸ τῆ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> ἀδελφῆς τοῦ πάππου μου κατὰ <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὸν</supplied> πατέρα Ἀννοῦ-

    <lb n="8"/>τος, ἣν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἔ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δ</supplied>ει μᾶλλον ἑτέρους κωλύειν ἐπὰν ἀδικίαν κατ᾽ ἐμοῦ διαπράξωσιν· 

    <lb n="9"/>αὕτη γὰρ ἐ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">π</supplied>οφθαλμήσασα τοῖς ἀ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρεσ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>οῖς θρέμ<add place="supralinear">μ</add>ασιν τοῖς πατρικοῖς μου νῦν <choice><corr>πρώτως</corr><sic>πρωτος</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="10"/>ἐπέρχετα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>, ἕρμαιον δηλον<add place="supralinear">ό</add>τι ἡ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">γη</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear>αμένη τὸν θάνατον τοῦ πατρός μ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ου</supplied>, πρὸς ὃν περι-

    <lb n="11"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied>ντα οὐδεμίαν μέμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ψι</supplied>ν πε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πο</supplied>ίηται οὐδὲ κινήσασα περὶ τοῦ 

    <lb n="12"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τ</supplied>υχό<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>τος, ἤδη εἰς γῆρας <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μα</unclear>κρὸν <choice><corr>ἐληλυθυῖα</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">εληλυθηια</add><del rend="corrected">εληλυθησα</del></subst></sic></choice>· ὑπὲρ γὰρ τὰ ἑ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ξ</supplied>ήκοντα  <num value="60"/> <subst><add place="inline">ἔτη</add><del rend="corrected">ε<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>η</del></subst> 

    <lb n="13"/>φαίνε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ται</supplied> βιώσασα, ἐν οἷς <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὰς</supplied> ἡσυχίας ἤγαγεν ἄχρι τοῦ παρόντος. διὸ — 

    <lb n="14"/>φανερο<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῦ</supplied> ὄντος περιττῶς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied>ῦν μεμνῆσθαι ὧν μὴ <choice><corr>ἐνῆξε</corr><sic>ενηξαι</sic></choice> μήτε πρὸς τὸν 

    <lb n="15"/>πάππ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ν μου, οὗ ἀδελφή ἐ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">σ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τι</supplied>ν, μήτε πρὸς τὸν <choice><corr>πατέρα</corr><sic>πατεραν</sic></choice> μου — δέομαι τῆς σῆς 

    <lb n="16"/>ἀρετῆς κελεῦσαι, ἐάν σοι δοκῇ, τὴν <choice><corr>παιδείαν</corr><sic>παιδιαν</sic></choice> τῆς γυναικὸς ἀποκοπῆναι 

    <lb n="17"/>δι᾽ οὗ ἐὰ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> δοκιμάσῃς — καὶ γὰ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρ</supplied> ὁ πατήρ μου τρεῖς σιτολογίας ἐξετέλεσεν, ὑπὲρ ὧν 

    <lb n="18"/>χρεώσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ης ἐστίν — καὶ τούτου <choice><corr>τυχὼν</corr><sic>τυχον</sic></choice> διὰ παντὸς χάριτάς σοι ὁμολογήσω.           διευτύχει. 

    <lb n="19"/>Αὐρήλιος <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Αἰ</unclear>τίοπας δι᾽ ἐμοῦ κηδεμόνος ἐπιδέδωκα. Αὐρήλιος Ἀγαθὸς ἔγραψα ὑπὲρ αὐτο<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ῦ</unclear> 

    <lb n="20"/>γράμματα μὴ εἰδότος. <del rend="erasure"><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear></del> Παῧνι <num value="16">ιϛ</num>. 

    <lb n="21"/>τῷ ἐν καθέξει ὄντ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ι</unclear> τὸ ἀβίαστον 

    <lb n="22"/>φυλάξει ὁ λογιστής. <expan>κόλλ<ex cert="high">ημα</ex></expan> <num value="65">ξε</num> 

    <lb n="23"/><expan>τόμο<ex cert="high">υ</ex></expan> <num value="2">β</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="0321" notBefore="0318" type="textDate">318 - 321</date></p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zur Datierung vgl. CPR V  7, Komm.  zu Z. 2. Tag: 10. Juni.</p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Sakaon</title><biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">13059</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0199</series>; ; <biblScope type="numbers">40</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0199;;40" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">300/301</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p><bibl type="illustration">Plate 9</bibl></p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Thead. 19</bibl></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Theadelphia</placeName> (<geogName cert="high" type="nome">Arsinoites</geogName>), <geogName cert="high" key="Aegyptus" type="ancientRegion">Egypt</geogName></p></div><div n="meta.13059" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Sakaon&amp;vVol=&amp;vNum=40"><fig